headline: Firefly Aerospace: From landing on the moon to landing on Wall St.
summary: Firefly Aerospace (FLY) is going public, making its Wall Street debut on the Nasdaq (NDAQ). CEO Jason Kim talks to Yahoo Finance Executive Editor Brian Sozzi about the company's ambitions, landing on the moon, and going public. To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Market Catalysts.
